parameters: I'm not done searching this room yet.
It was foolish of me to think we'd find Isaac so easily...
But maybe we can still find some clues as to where he might have gone.

They don't even look used yet either.\! Must be a new topic.
Hey Nadia.\! Is Isaac really smart or something?\! These textbooks look intense.
He is actually!\! \BST[1]Isaac's always been in advanced academics from a young age.
Our parents always put a strong focus on education while we were growing up.
So that's why I don't recognize this room.\! It's the class for geniuses, huh?
This class is actually his homeroom.
He told me that because of his test scores, he was placed in this class with other gifted students.
That's impressive.\! \BST[2]I was way less interested in textbooks and more on
He's a smart boy, but he doesn't apply himself as much as he should.
Hah hah!\! If I had some Æµ every time my counselor told me that, I'd be rich!
I think you and Isaac would get along pretty well then.
This plant looks so well taken care of!
That brings back such wonderful memories!
Do you like gardening or something?
Nope!\! My thumbs definitely aren't green.
But I used to study medicine and phytotherapy.
Whoa, you must be super smart then!
There were definitely a lot of late nights studying.
But my parents have always inspired me to study hard!
Last year, however, I got to work with some students who were studying botany.
One of the students in particular was so lovely!
She was brilliant.\! Painfully shy, but passionate about her studies never the less.
Oh yeah?\! What was her name?
Hm, I don't know a Natasha.\! \BST[1]But she sounds very nice.
I hope she's staying safe somewhere out there...

Doesn't that seem a little weird to you, \n[1]?

Maybe I can find some useful information here...
I'm sure something in here can be useful.
I don't understand it.\! Take a look at this.
It only shows Isaac's name on it.
He's the only student listed here.
You mean he's in a homeroom class with only one student in it?!
That just can't be right.\! It doesn't make any sense.
But so many things about this classroom are so off...
*gasp*\! Nadia.\! I think I know what's going on!
We must be in the wrong classroom!
Well, this is his homeroom...\! He didn't make that up.
And besides, his name is the only one that's actually on this roster anyway!
Now I know what's going on.\! Let me explain...
The attendance sheet has a big typo on it!
I bet his teacher accidentally deleted all of the other student's names on here.
That theory...\! I'm sorry but it just doesn't make any sense at all.
*Urgh*\! [She shot down my idea even though I was so confident!]

\n[1]...\! This isn't the time to be joking around!

And the hottest teacher on the planet!

Flirting around with a teacher of all people?!

I mean, maybe that's not what's going on and it's just a misunderstanding.
But most importantly, it doesn't really help us find out where he is.
That's true.\! We still didn't find any leads to where he could have gone.
We've been searching around here for a while.\! It's probably best that we head back home now.

On second thought, maybe I should just pretend I didn't see anything here...

Yeah.\! I do recall hearing her name now that you mention it.
Do you remember her from your time as a student?
